;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a86606582130fda391dd2393857bd50d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/walleeatssmoothies/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">walleeatssmoothies</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">février 12, 2022</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I use this for my website and it has reliably worked for sometime. I like it and depend on it. Highly recommend if you are willing to play around / sit through tutorials to learn more about how to make the most use out of it.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Good</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/iyan02/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1b4b99bd88be7c4474dc286b1d351a20?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1b4b99bd88be7c4474dc286b1d351a20?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/iyan02/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">iyan02</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">février 11, 2022</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">cihuy!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\